<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Metodo Podomoro</title>
</head>

<body style="background-color: #565488;">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
            <img src="/docs/4.4/assets/brand/bootstrap-solid.svg" width="30" height="30"
                class="d-inline-block align-top" alt="">
            Metodo Podomoro
        </a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <ul class="nav flex-column h4">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link w-50 p-2" href="/">Pomodoro</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link w-50 p-2" href="/corto">Descanso Corto</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link w-50 p-2" href="/largo">Descanso Largo</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-10">
                <div class="card" style="background-color: #00b7d4;">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <p class="text-monospace h1">{{perfil}}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body" style="background-color: #2f3f80;">
                        <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
                        <p class="text-capitalize text-center text-warning">NO PUEDES HACER OTRA TAREA POR 25 MIN.</p>
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col">
                                    <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
                                        <div class="col col-lg-2">
                                            <button id="iniciar" type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-block">Iniciar</button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col col-lg-2">
                                            <button id="reiniciar" type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-block">Reinciar</button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col col-lg-2">
                                            <button id="parar" type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-block">Parar</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <br>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col text-center">
                                    <div>
                                        <span class="h1 text-white" id="minutos">{{min}}</span><span class="h1 text-white">:</span><span class="h1 text-white" id="segundos">{{seg}}</span> 
                                        
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="container">
                            <br>
                            <br>
                        </div>
                        <footer class="blockquote-footer">"Somos el resultado de lo que hacemos repetidamente. La excelencia entonces, no es un acto, sino un habito."<cite title="Source Title">- Arist√≥teles</cite></footer>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/crono.js"></script>
</body>

</html>